Author: Selacoulerdouce
Title: [ANN]ICO IS LIVE🚀UBCOIN - EXCHANGE CRYPTOCURRENCY FOR REAL GOODS🚀
Body: 🔥 We are introducing reasonable commissions for making purchases in ETH  2% for buying something on Ubcoin Market using ethers, paid by buyer.  💎 We want to keep balance between using 2 currencies on the marketplace: UBC and ETH. ETH is more widespread, but now it is cheaper to use UBC.  Why did we introduce ETH as an alternative means of payment on Ubcoin Market? Because we see our mission, beside other things, in stimulating people to regard crypto currencies not only as a speculative investment. Using crypto is cheaper and faster than using traditional currencies via banking systems. Crypto is not only something “that can make me rich in a few days”, it is also something “I can use as a means of payment more convenient than dollar”. And we are creating an ecosystem where this particular value of digital currencies can be very well perceived.  These thoughts were also inspired by a recent, widely discussed Reddit post "Why Nobody Talks About Financial Incentives For Average People To Use Crypto?”. It says: "Whenever people discuss cryptocurrencies, it's almost always about "should I invest in this thing? It can go up to $xxxxx, right?”…But when you tell average people in the real world that they can "save $xxx money" by pointing out how expensive our current cross-border transaction through the banking system is, they would start listening.”. https://www.reddit.com/r/CryptoCurrency/comments/abh0kd/why_nobody_talks_about_financial_incentives_for/?st=JQEY9GPD&sh=2ab1165c  ❤️ One of the goals of the Ubcoin marketplace is to show people how crypto can be used - and used conveniently - outside the world of speculations. And with introducing ETH - one of the most popular digital currencies in the world - we can show it even better.

Author: Betay
Title: [ANN]ICO IS LIVE🚀UBCOIN - EXCHANGE CRYPTOCURRENCY FOR REAL GOODS🚀
Body: We are NOT similar to other projects, we are absolutely unique compared to other platforms. So, there are two businesses you could possible compare us: 1) Crypro-Goods Exchange. Ebay is the closest example. We are not competing with that business, though we are using the same way of selling and buying goods - but the audience and purpose of that buy/sell operations are - to INVEST or EXIT in crypto. So, if a person wants to sell his iPad and get USD - he always goes to Ebay. But a person wants to become investor in Crypto and all other ways are complicated fot him - he uses an ordinary way - selling anything. 2) Exchanges. Bitfinex is the closest example. We are taking the idea of investing. But the main difference is that in classic exchange you need other currency to exchange it to crypto and back. Exchange will set limits and you’ll need to pass KYC, as they are dealing with real money.

Author: Betay
Title: [ANN]ICO IS LIVE🚀UBCOIN - EXCHANGE CRYPTOCURRENCY FOR REAL GOODS🚀
Body: I hope this answers your earlier question:  Excellent question. Step 1: say what you're going to do and do what you said you were going to do. We will deliver the product according to our roadmap and timeline. Step 2: Intrinsic utility value. The tokens hold intrinsic value as a means of settlement on the marketplace, paying fees and setting commission schedules. Hype evaporates, and real demand and supply stays. We spend the proceeds on developing the technology and on bringing large number of users to the marketplace, thus increasing utility demand for the token. Step 3: Assets are worth something if they exhibit liquidity. For that, we are listing UBC on leading exchanges to allow frictionless buying and selling of UBC. Step 4: Protect your investors: Supply of tokens is limited, it's not minable. No new tokens are released by the company at prices undercutting ICO investors. Step 5: Manage volatility. A reserve pool of tokens is set aside to allow to mitigate possible volatility or concerted efforts to manipulate UBC exchange rate, as a protection against pump-and-dump schemes. Step 6: Reward your investors: Up to 10% of the platforms net operating income will be spent on buying back tokens in the market. Step 7: Increase scarcity of tokens: 5% of all fees collected by Ubcoin from transactions in UBC will be irrevocably burned, thus diminishing supply of tokens and increasing the value of the remaining tokens. Ultimately, from value standpoint, crypto tokens are favorably distinguished from fiat in that they are not subject to inflation or blatant government printing, and from minable coins - that the supply is predetermined and calculable, which provides a clear algorithm for setting the value of the tokens.

Author: Betay
Title: [ANN]ICO IS LIVE🚀UBCOIN - EXCHANGE CRYPTOCURRENCY FOR REAL GOODS🚀
Body: Smart contract requires both parties to sign off on settlement of the transaction. The platform holds buyer’s funds in escrow while goods are in transit. Once received, if the goods are not of described quality or condition, the buyer’s funds are not released to the seller. If parties fail to settle amicably on their own, then the platform provides a two-tier dispute arbitration service.   First tier of arbitration consists of two selected Ubcoin users with high enough rating and relevant to the geography, product, type of sale that is in dispute. If the dispute parties are not satisfied with the user arbitration, it goes to the second-tier — a Ubcoin arbiter who is a support staff member of Ubcoin. Funds/goods are released to the party found wronged by non-performance of the other party. Guilty party’s rating on the platform is decreased. Repeat offenders are suspended for a limited time. Worst offenders are banned from the platform. User of the platform are motivated to act as arbiters by a small fee reward and increased profile/user rating for quality arbitration. High user ratings qualify the user for preferential platform fee schedule and access to more premium features of the marketplace.

Author: Betay
Title: [ANN]ICO IS LIVE🚀UBCOIN - EXCHANGE CRYPTOCURRENCY FOR REAL GOODS🚀
Body: Cross-border is definitely a big option. Over 25% of transactions in marketplaces these days occur between different countries. Users will see shipping options available in the marketplace. If Alibaba and Amazon taught us anything is that cross-border shipping doesn’t mean expensive. May take a bit longer and not all goods can be shipped, but overall it’s a healthy mix of local and cross-border trade. Besides, you know that there are great price disparities between different countries for same types of goods, even with shipping it is often cheaper to buy some things in Korea or China and have them sent to Germany or the U.S. The entire transaction is settled in UBC, but if shipping is involved, the seller will the charge pay his local shipping company directly in fiat, but the price he receives for the goods is in UBC and covers estimated shipping. Our roadmap sees an open API to be released in 2019 that shipping companies can use if they want to start accepting pmt in UBC and integrate seamlessly with Ubcoin Marketplace.

Author: Betay
Title: [ANN]ICO IS LIVE🚀UBCOIN - EXCHANGE CRYPTOCURRENCY FOR REAL GOODS🚀
Body: Summary of Long-Term Value Enhancing Measures Ubcoin token is native to the peer-to-peer marketplace ecosystem. Smart contracts will not accept any other cryptocurrency for facilitating transactions in the marketplace. As volume of sales and purchases on the marketplace grows, demand for Ubcoin token will organically increase. Long term value for those tokens starts at utility and their price also relies on supply and demand. In order to manage supply, help reduce volatility and enable persons who need UBC to obtain them, Ubcoin has created a five-pronged approach: 1) The creation of a Reserve Pool, as described in previous section, ensuring that no new tokens may enter into circulation at prices lower than those paid during Token Sale. 2) We intend that holders of Ubcoin tokens will be offered discounts on fees based on their overall UBC holdings. The more UBC they own, the higher the discount will be. This will likely incentivize clients to buy and hold UBC, further reducing the available supply. 3) Reasonable vesting and anti-dumping prevention mechanisms, as set in previous section. 4) The creation of a Token Buyback Program, funded with up to 10% of Ubcoins’s net operating profits annually. 5) The creation of Burn Program, which will methodically reduce supply the more successful the business becomes.   The details of items 4 and 5 are outline as follows below: • Token Buyback Program  The UBC Buyback Program, funded with up to 10% of Ubcoins’s net operating profits annually, will be created. Ubcoin intends to use the UBC Buyback Program to support the stability of UBC on the exchanges as needed. To facilitate liquidity on both buy and sell sides, UBC bought back by Ubcoin will be sold onto the exchange as needed depending on the underlying demand. A key feature of the buyback program is that the buyback offer price is: the larger of (a) token purchase price during private limited pre-sale or public token sale, or (b) current market price, (c) and the larger value multiplied by a factor of 1.1. 46  IMPORTANT: Net Operating Profit here refers to net operating profits once Ubcoin is fully operational and does not in any way relate to the sums collected by way of the scheduled Pre-Sale or Token Sale. Purchasers have no rights in respect of the Token Buyback Reserve and the use of the profits is at Ubcoin’s discretion and control. It is also subject to applicable legal and regulatory requirements. Gauging the possible size of this reserve is difficult at the outset of the initial Token Sale. Projections may generally be based on market size and capitalization, as well as speculation based on published data from competitors and general market research.

Author: Betay
Title: [ANN]ICO IS LIVE🚀UBCOIN - EXCHANGE CRYPTOCURRENCY FOR REAL GOODS🚀
Body: "We are not only NOT similar, we are absolutley unique compared to other platforms. So there are two businesses you could possible compare us:        1) Marketplace. Ebay is the closest example. We are not compiting with that business, though we are using the same way of selling and buying goods - but the audience and purpose of that buy/sell operations are - to INVEST or EXIT in crypto. So if a person wants to sell his iPad and get USD - he always goes to Ebay. But  a person wants to become investor in Crypto and all other ways are complicated fot him - he uses an ordinary way - selling anything. 2) Exchanges. Bitfinex is the closest example. We are taking the idea of investing. But the main difference is that in classic exchange you need other currency to exchange it to crypto and back. Exchange will set limits and you’ll need to pass KYC, as they are dealing with real money."

Author: Betay
Title: [ANN]ICO IS LIVE🚀UBCOIN - EXCHANGE CRYPTOCURRENCY FOR REAL GOODS🚀
Body: There is some info from the press releases published in various media: “Huawei, the global developer of ICT solutions, will now be releasing smartphones with the pre-installed mobile application uBank. All Huawei smartphones, including Ascend and Honor of the latest modifications, will be equipped with a payment service, CNews told uBank. Owners of Huawei smartphones with pre-installed uBank will be able to pay for goods, mobile communications, internet, television, housing and utilities and other services from both the internal account of the application and the attached bank card. With the help of the service, users can ask for a loan from a friend or transfer money, as well as repay a loan. Payment for many services in the application is made without commission”. According to uBank, Huawei is the third mobile device manufacturer, with which uBank cooperates after Samsung and Fly.

Ebay is the closest example. So if a person wants to sell his iPad and get USD - he always goes to Ebay. But  a person wants to become investor in Crypto and all other ways are complicated fot him - he uses an ordinary way - selling anything. 2) Exchanges. Bitfinex is the closest example. Body: Long term value for those tokens starts at utility and their price also relies on supply and demand. In order to manage supply, help reduce volatility and enable persons who need UBC to obtain them, Ubcoin has created a five-pronged approach: 1) The creation of a Reserve Pool, as described in previous section, ensuring that no new tokens may enter into circulation at prices lower than those paid during Token Sale. 2) We intend that holders of Ubcoin tokens will be offered discounts on fees based on their overall UBC holdings. The more UBC they own, the higher the discount will be. This will likely incentivize clients to buy and hold UBC, further reducing the available supply. 3) Reasonable vesting and anti-dumping prevention mechanisms, as set in previous section. 4) The creation of a Token Buyback Program, funded with up to 10% of Ubcoins’s net operating profits annually. 5) The creation of Burn Program, which will methodically reduce supply the more successful the business becomes.

Body: You can follow us on Telegram and approach the team there: https://t.me/ubcoin   Quote from: rdizza on March 16, 2018, 07:08:11 PM My child often uses my phone. Will I be able adjust in the way preventing the goods from "adults only" category from being displayed  on the main screen?  Yes. Parental lock and Locked categories feature will allow to customize access and presentation of information in the app. Additionally, pre-screening of seller postings using ML and AI technologies will prevent objectionable material from appearing in the app   Quote from: woodcoin on April 05, 2018, 11:50:03 PM Will it be possible to purchase UBcoin tokens via online banking? This would significantly expand the audience of potential investors.  Online banking relies on processing companies such as Visa, Mastercard or SWIFT. While it is absolutely logical that option to buy Ubcoin via online banking would greatly increase the reach of the project, it is not viable as these giant processors and banks are struggling to adopt blockchain technology, fear the repercussions of uncertain regulative climate regarding cryptocurrency. Overall, we believe in the future we will get there, but for now the easiest way to get into crypto will be by buying and selling goods in exchange for crypto. Ubcoin aims to bring this mechanism to anyone with a smartphone in their hands anywhere in the world.  Quote from: app2endad on April 06, 2018, 01:19:14 AM If I use one device with other family members, can we quickly switch between accounts?  You can set account access options, including PIN-protection, forced inactive session sign-out, family-access option.   Quote from: robinzzon on April 05, 2018, 10:20:03 PM Good evening. It seems to me that you could reduce the release of tokens without compromising their functionality. How do you like this idea?  If this is a question about the total supply number of tokens, it should be noted that only paid-for tokens will be issued. Therefore the market will truly determine what is the optimal number of tokens to be issued. The shares of tokens attributable to non-public distribution (i.e. team, advisors, community, etc) are pro-rated based on the number of tokens actually sold at the public token sale event. In essence, it's a self-regulating smart contract for determining the optimal number of tokens to be issued.  Quote from: robinzzon on March 16, 2018, 09:26:05 PM Hi. What market share do you expect to take by 2023? It's important for me to understand whether you have a clear plan.  That's an awesome question. Many see us competing with your typical online marketplaces, but that's not really accurate. But for discussion sake, let's take a look at that train of thought: 2016 Gross Merchandise Value (GMV) sold on on all online marketplaces was $1.085 trillion. By 2022, GMS is expected to reach $3.3 trillion. We forecast our GMV to hit $2.5 billion in 2022, that's 0,08% of the total value of goods sold. However, and it is a critical distinction, our target audience is not those who buy and sell on marketplaces for fiat, but those who (a) want to own crypto and seek an easy entry into it, and (b) those who own crypto and want to spend it. With that market segment in mind, there are expected to be about 200 million active wallets by 2022, and we forecast our audience to reach 30.8 million buyers and sellers, which by that measurement would give us market share of engaged crypto users of 15.4%.

Author: Betay
Title: [ANN]ICO IS LIVE🚀UBCOIN - EXCHANGE CRYPTOCURRENCY FOR REAL GOODS🚀
Body: Excellent question. Step 1: say what you're going to do and do what you said you were going to do. We will deliver the product according to our roadmap and timeline. Step 2: Intrinsic utility value. The tokens hold intrinsic value as a means of settlement on the marketplace, paying fees and setting commission schedules. Hype evaporates, and real demand and supply stays. We spend the proceeds on developing the technology and on bringing large number of users to the marketplace, thus increasing utility demand for the token. Step 3: Assets are worth something if they exhibit liquidity. For that, we are listing UBC on leading exchanges to allow frictionless buying and selling of UBC. Step 4: Protect your investors: Supply of tokens is limited, it's not minable. No new tokens are released by the company at prices undercutting ICO investors. Step 5: Manage volatility. A reserve pool of tokens is set aside to allow to mitigate possible volatility or concerted efforts to manipulate UBC exchange rate, as a protection against pump-and-dump schemes. Step 6: Reward your investors: Up to 10% of the platforms net operating income will be spent on buying back tokens in the market. Step 7: Increase scarcity of tokens: 5% of all fees collected by Ubcoin from transactions in UBC will be irrevocably burned, thus diminishing supply of tokens and increasing the value of the remaining tokens.  Ultimately, from value standpoint, crypto tokens are favorably distinguished from fiat in that they are not subject to inflation or blatant government printing, and from minable coins - that the supply is predetermined and calculable, which provides a clear algorithm for setting the value of the tokens.

Author: Betay
Title: [ANN]ICO IS LIVE🚀UBCOIN - EXCHANGE CRYPTOCURRENCY FOR REAL GOODS🚀
Body: Regulation of previously unregulated industries, as history shows, exponentially increases the industry and market size. The reason for that is the removal of many risks and uncertainties inherent in WildWest-type markets. As risks are removed, the industry becomes more appealing to mass consumers and institutional investors. Therefore, we welcome regulation of the industry. However, we believe that regulation of crypto world may differ quite substantially since crypto and blockchain are based on decentralization, which is the antithesis of regulation. Therefore, our initial focus is peer-to-peer transactions, which do not rely as much on solid regulation. We envision bringing onboard small and medium enterprises in about 1 years time as rules become more transparent in terms of taxation, accounting, legal enforcement. Big businesses will come later once major risks are removed.

Ubcoin Market offers a solution for two clear-cut and objective opportunities. The first opportunity stems from almost 2 billion digital citizens, many of whom are keenly interested in cryptocurrency but have their path to crypto investment hindered by technological and legal barriers: mining is expensive and changing fiat money to cryptocurrencies is a cumbersome process. Author: ber68dclass
Title: [ANN]ICO IS LIVE🚀UBCOIN - EXCHANGE CRYPTOCURRENCY FOR REAL GOODS🚀
Body: The Ubcoin Market project is happy to announce that we have changed the amount of minimal contribution from 50 ETH to 5 ETH during current Limited Private Pre-Sale Stage of ICO.  The discount on Token Price is still 57%. The Pre-Sale Stage will last till March, 31 on these terms.  The Pre-Sale Stage started on March, 10. Since then we received a considerable number of requests from people who would like to take part in the pre-sale and invest a substantial amount of money but were still finding 50 ETH being too weighty.  At the same time we came to the conclusion that 50 ETH as a minimum transaction combined with a great discount on token price might lead to the situation where a little number of large investors holded too many UBC tokens and had the ability to influence the stability of the UBC cryptocurrency.  Taking all these considerations into account we decided to reduce the amount of minimal contribution at the pre-sale stage from 50 ETH to 5 ETH keeping the discount being the same (57%). Any people willing to take part in Ubcoin ICO under these conditions are able do it till March, 31.  We hope that it will increase the number of private buyers of UBC tokens and help our intention to make Ubcoin Market a truly mass product.  If you are interested to invest 5+ ETH and get UBC tokens with 57% discount (1 ETH = 18,667 UBC) please contact us at hello@ubcoin.io

Author: ber68dclass
Title: [ANN]ICO IS LIVE🚀UBCOIN - EXCHANGE CRYPTOCURRENCY FOR REAL GOODS🚀
Body: A Team Leader within Samsung has Joined the Ubcoin Market Project    Oleg Bud is a team leader at Samsung Electronics. He will share his knowledge and expertise in the field of product development and global marketing for Ubcoin’s market endeavour. Samsung has been a reliable and long-standing partner of the team that is behind the Ubcoin project. So it’s a genuine pleasure to see one of its talented staff among the team’s advisers.  Ubcoin market is a platform where anyone can become a cryptocurrency investor. All you need is a possession you are ready to sell. Just set a price and receive the crypto money for it! Additionally, you can purchase goods and services using your crypto cash.  To make the market available to as many users as possible, we will integrate it within our Ubank application that has currently about 7 years of successful business life and has been downloaded 16 million times. Ubank is also one of the most popular apps in CIS.  The project already has a significant history of collaboration with Samsung. Since 2013 every Samsung and Fly mobile phone in CIS market has a Ubank application pre-installed . Furthermore, the founder and investor of Ubcoin Andrew Lee has a strong business relationship with Samsung. The above stated are just a few reasons why we are especially glad to see one more of Samsung’s employees among our advisers.  Oleg Bud has proven himself as a talented expert both in the fields of product development and marketing. His expertise involve finding the best customer solutions, and presenting them in a convincing manner. Moreover, his shrewdness within the marketing sphere has given him a great reputation. He is the person behind an ambitious Samsung Pay project, the most prominent Samsung mobile flagship and Bada platform’s launch in CIS countries.  The project team believes Oleg’s contributions will aid in the success of Ubcoin’s endeavors. His experience as a team leader at Samsung Electronics is sure to bring value to the project as well as utility to every user.  Oleg supports Ubcoin Market and believes that the project can and will significantly contribute to mass popularity of cryptocurrency.  When we asked Oleg his opinion on the matter he stated: “This project has a rare connection of virtual blockchain based financing and real world goods. That makes it promising way to look for both: those who would like to easily enter cryptocurrency world and those who would like to exchange their crypto earnings on some real world product. Actually that service provides basic from where all economics starts. It justifies a crypto money by adding a bit of the real world value”.  Oleg Bud’s joining of the Ubcoin team is a welcome though expected step in the cooperation between our team and Samsung. We are glad and proud to have Oleg Bud as our adviser.
